title: Jazz Moods - Jazz at Love's End 1999 [Jazz][mp3 3
description:
Jazz Moods - Jazz at Love's End 
Original Release Date: September 14, 1999 
Audio CD: September 14, 1999 
Label: Concord Records 
Bitrate: 320 kbps

Many entries in the Jazz Moods compilation series try to create their atmospheres mostly with instrumentals, but Jazz Moods: Jazz at Love's End approaches its subject with vocal renditions of 11 heartbreak ballads. Individual songs can range from sentimental and sweet to sad and forlorn, but the musical feel tends to cohere pretty well, making the collection perfect for those late-night wallows in sadness following a breakup. ~ Steve Huey, AMG

Jazz Moods - Jazz at Love's End Tracks:
01 Karrin Allyson - Good Morning Heartache
02 Ernestine Anderson - Welcome To The Club
03 Dennis Rowland - You Don't Know What Love Is
04 Rosemary Clooney With The Count Basie Orchestra - The Man That Got Away
05 Mary Stallings - I Waited For You
06 Mel Torm'e - If You Could See Me Now
07 Jack Mcduff - Cry Me A River
08 Dennis Rowland - Angel Eyes
09 Carol Sloane - I'll Be Around
10 Marlena Shaw - Where Do You Start
11 Susannah Mccorkle - They Can't Take That Away From Me
